{
  "title": "How to add a certificate to a DMCS",
  "slug": "how-to-add-a-certificate-to-a-dmcs",
  "categorySlug": "it-onboarding",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How to add a certificate to a DMCS</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">This article is for ubuntu admins only</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>Before you start - make sure you have acquired a .pfx certificate for the proper domain as well as the password for the .pfx certificate.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Make sure the domain points to the external domain of the DMCS. If the DMCS is not available on the internet - make sure that you have a local DNS service to validate the certificate</p>\n<div>Guide for certificate setup:</div>\n<ol data-stringify-type=\"ordered-list\" data-indent=\"0\" data-border=\"0\">\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Upload certificate to server: scp -i ~/.ssh/yourpem.pem Downloads/certifickatname.pfx adminling@dmccsdoamin/home/myfolder</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Find location of certs folder:&nbsp;docker volume inspect certs</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Move pfx file from home dir to certs dir: mv /home/myfolder/certficatename.pfx /mnt/docker/volumes/certs/_data/</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Go to certs dir:&nbsp;cd /mnt/docker/volumes/certs/_data/</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Rename pfx file: mv cdertifikatname.pfx cert.pfx</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Unpack pfx: openssl&nbsp;pkcs12 -in cert.pfx -nocerts -out key.pem</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Unpack cert:&nbsp;openssl pkcs12 -in cert.pfx -clcerts -nokeys -out cert.pem</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Unpack key:&nbsp;openssl rsa -in key.pem -out server.key</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Rename cert:&nbsp;mv cert.pem fullchain.pem</li>\n<li data-stringify-indent=\"0\" data-stringify-border=\"0\">Rename key:&nbsp;mv server.key privkey.pem</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/how-to-add-a-certificate-to-a-dmcs"
}